{
  "stem": "16140.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Poland, we went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from Germany, we came to Canada.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't live there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We moved to the city where-- where the government has their offices.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because everybody that survived lived there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not particularly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the other survivors stayed in the city, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we stayed in the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [LAUGHS] it was just too bad nothing was left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took everything out of the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was think that was there was food-- was all kinds of food and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took it all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They emptied it all out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Nazi-- the Nazi police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a house.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were so many empty houses, [LAUGHS] you could move into any house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was houses and no people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, quite a few, some young girls, some-- the Mani Schwartzman came back and Barbara Schwartzman with the-- the [? praises ?] of the Judenrat children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All gone to Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the Polish people weren't there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were going to school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were a lot of Ukrainian students, some were Russian girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some girls came from Russia to study, Moscow from Leningrad to study at this university.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we decided to go when-- it came a lot that all the Polish citizens before the war are afraid to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From Poland, we went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From Germany, we came to Canada.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because mostly Jewish people were emigrating to-- to Canada, the states or Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, I mean, everybody is doing what everybody else is doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
